high_descs: Turn to the right and walk towards the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap in the tub.
Go to the right and place the bar of soup in the sink.
Fill the sink up with water and remove the soap.
Turn to the left and walk towards the toilet.
Place the soap on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place the soap from the tub on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the right side of the bath tub.
Take the pink soap to the right of the rag from the bath tub.
Go to the sink to the right of the bath tub.
Wash the soap in the sink. Take the soap from the sink.
Turn left, go to the toilet on the other side of the bathroom.
Put the soap on top of the tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the tank of a toilet.

high_descs: Walk over to the foot of the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap in the bath tub.
Walk around to face the sink at the foot of the bath tub.
Put the soap in the sink and run some water and then remove the soap.
Walk around the tub to the toilet on the other side of the room.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet next to the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Wash a bar of soap in the sink, as well as place it on the toilet.

high_descs: turn around and walk forwards a bit, then turn left and walk over to the bathtub on the left
grab the soap out of the bathtub
turn right and walk to the end of the room, and then turn left and walk over to the sink
wash the soap out in the sink, then pick it back up
turn around and walk to the toilet on the right side of the room
place the soap on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: placed rinsed off soap on top of the toilet
